{"tid":2011252,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"覺唔覺得係捉灑d人係為23條鋪路","createTime":"2020-05-11T00:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T01:30:50.000Z","uid":184099,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb77eabd4c56f8601fcbd973753dba9ab503aa8c","tid":2011252,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:53:37.000Z","msg":"反修例明顯試水溫，<br />\n引蛇出動，<br />\n你以為佢地步步都行錯，<br />\n其實係用黎不停圍捕肯出黎行既人。<br />\n圍捕最核心既勇武。<br />\n<br />\n捉灑核心反抗既人，<br />\n到時23條立法就無人行。<br />\n就無勇武，<br />\n然後就順利。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">23條永遠都係boss。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n國歌法，逃犯條例呢d都係要你犯法，<br />\n但23條係老屈法律，23條過基本上等同所以惡法都通過。<br />\n<br />\n希望到時23條立法既時候仲會有人出黎行。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71277c3c5ee3113fab820dfc78ebcd429c91c8ed","tid":2011252,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/96573117_913329422425107_462302707714097152_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=ca434c&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkfIHtZm93dUmglt6SCeGpVvMZH6cHuHv4enhII2dOTXKyjQ04Mhzkdxqn1mxZY9dU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=14&amp;oh=14110ffb4b6f6dce78d744b53152fb70&amp;oe=5EDFBB1D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F96573117_913329422425107_462302707714097152_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3Dca434c%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkfIHtZm93dUmglt6SCeGpVvMZH6cHuHv4enhII2dOTXKyjQ04Mhzkdxqn1mxZY9d